  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Industrial Engineering</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kembangan</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.30am – 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $3,400 + Performance Incentive + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and follow up on new sales opportunities across different sectors</li><li>Provide technical advice and recommend suitable products to clients</li><li>Prepare quotations, proposals, and presentations</li><li>Build and maintain strong customer relationships</li><li>Conduct site visits and product demonstrations</li><li>Work with internal teams and suppliers to meet customer needs</li><li>Stay updated on market trends, products, and competitors</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Engineering (Mechanical, Civil, or related fields)</li><li>Sales or technical experience in industrial or engineering products is preferred</li><li>Strong communication and presentation skills</li><li>Self-driven, resourceful, and able to work independently</li><li>Possession of a Class 3 driving licence is an advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78821 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
